channel.title: The Celebrity Traitors
channel.desc: As the ultimate reality game of detection, treachery and trust continues, the celebrity Players realise that the mission is not only high stakes, but could also hold important information in their hunt for the Traitors. With the sun setting, the first Round Table commences, and emotions run high as the players' suspicions are put to the test, but are they looking at the right people?
